Class RequestEditShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • messages.RequestModifyShape

  • public class RequestEditShape
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to store data of the request from the client if editShape in RESTHandler gets called and the user wants to change the Shape. It is necessary to access the data of the JSON object/body which the server receives from the client.
    See Also:
    RESTHandler, ProjectService

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      RequestEditShape(int layerIndex, int shapeIndex, Shape shape)
